<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs><rs type="objectType"> lintel</rs> block, slightly damaged at right end (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">2.16</measure>), with egg and dart moulding above three fasciae.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in one line on all three fasciae (heights <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.09</measure>, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.08</measure>, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.06</measure>)</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Striking hand, with omicron and theta half the size of the upright letters; l.1, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.055</measure>; ll.2, 3, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0138" notBefore="0117">A.D. 117-138</date> (<rs type="criteria">reign</rs>)
</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
